node.text:
Our little chonk Maxine is also a little monster and chews through most toys pretty quickly…until the @superchewer box.

We've had a hard time with dog toys -- not many are designed that well. Then the folks @Superchewer sent us one of their themed monthly boxes and honestly the toys are incredible.  Click the link in our bio to order your box and you'll get an additional $84 of free toys with a 6 month subscription. We can't recommend this subscription enough. @Superchewer #Superchewer #ad
